Database Design

TABLE CREATION

CREATE TABLE Sex ( SexID int PRIMARY KEY NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT, SexName varchar(255) ); CREATE TABLE Race ( RaceID int PRIMARY KEY NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT, RaceName varchar(255) ); CREATE TABLE RaceAndSex ( RaceAndSexID INT PRIMARY KEY NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT, SexID INT, RaceID INT, FOREIGN KEY (SexID) REFERENCES Sex(SexID), FOREIGN KEY (RaceID) REFERENCES Race(RaceID) ); CREATE TABLE CauseOfDeath ( CauseOfDeathID int PRIMARY KEY NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT, CauseOfDeathName varchar(255), CauseOfDeathNameFriendly varchar(255)); CREATE TABLE RaceAndSexAndCauseOfDeath ( RaceAndSexAndCauseOfDeathID INT PRIMARY KEY NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT, RaceAndSexID INT, CauseOfDeathID INT, AgeDied INT, FOREIGN KEY (RaceAndSexID) REFERENCES RaceAndSex(RaceAndSexID), FOREIGN KEY (CauseOfDeathID) REFERENCES CauseOfDeath(CauseOfDeathID) );

STORED PROCEDURES

DELIMITER // CREATE PROCEDURE InsertRaceAndSexAndCauseOfDeath (IN RaceAndSexID INT, IN CauseOfDeathID INT, IN AgeDied INT, IN NumDeaths INT) BEGIN DECLARE i INT; SET i = 0; WHILE i < NumDeaths DO INSERT INTO `RaceAndSexAndCauseOfDeath` (`RaceAndSexID`, `CauseOfDeathID`, `AgeDied`) VALUES (RaceAndSexID, CauseOfDeathID, AgeDied); SET i = i + 1; END While; END; // DELIMITER ;

DELIMITER // CREATE PROCEDURE GetDeathAgeAndCause (IN UserRaceSexID INT, IN UserAge INT) BEGIN SET @MinDeathID = ( SELECT RaceAndSexAndCauseOfDeathID AS MinRaceSexID FROM RaceAndSexAndCauseOfDeath WHERE RaceAndSexID = UserRaceSexID AND AgeDied = UserAge LIMIT 1 ); SET @MaxDeathID = ( SELECT RaceAndSexAndCauseOfDeathID AS MaxRaceSexID FROM RaceAndSexAndCauseOfDeath WHERE RaceAndSexID = UserRaceSexID GROUP BY RaceAndSexAndCauseOfDeathID DESC LIMIT 1 ); SET @RandDeathID = FLOOR(RAND()*(@MaxDeathID-@MinDeathID+1)+@MinDeathID); SET @UserAgeDied = (SELECT AgeDied FROM RaceAndSexAndCauseOfDeath WHERE RaceAndSexAndCauseOfDeathID = @RandDeathID); SET @MinCauseOfDeathID = ( SELECT RaceAndSexAndCauseOfDeathID AS MinCauseOfDeathID FROM RaceAndSexAndCauseOfDeath WHERE RaceAndSexID = UserRaceSexID AND AgeDied = @UserAgeDied GROUP BY RaceAndSexAndCauseOfDeathID LIMIT 1 ); SET @MaxCauseOfDeathID = ( SELECT RaceAndSexAndCauseOfDeathID AS MaxCauseOfDeathID FROM RaceAndSexAndCauseOfDeath WHERE RaceAndSexID = UserRaceSexID GROUP BY RaceAndSexAndCauseOfDeathID DESC LIMIT 1 ); SET @RandCauseOfDeathID = (FLOOR(RAND()*(@MaxCauseOfDeathID-@MinCauseOfDeathID+1)+@MinCauseOfDeathID)); SET @UserDeathID = (SELECT CauseOfDeathID FROM RaceAndSexAndCauseOfDeath rascod WHERE rascod.RaceAndSexAndCauseOfDeathID = @RandCauseOfDeathID LIMIT 1); SELECT @UserAgeDied, CauseOfDeathNameFriendly FROM CauseOfDeath cod WHERE cod.CauseOfDeathID = @UserDeathID; END; // DELIMITER ;
